rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 85 C0 74 ?? ?? ?? ?? 8D 95 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // Test EAX + JE + LEA (sandbox check)
        $pattern1 = { FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? 53 6A 40 53 68 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // CALL ExitProcess + PUSHs (direct exit)
        $pattern2 = { A8 01 75 ?? ?? ?? ?? FF 75 ?? FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // TEST AL + JNE + PUSH + CALL (bit check)

    condition:
        any of them
}
